<doc id="534502" wikidata="Q87237" url="?curid=534502" title="D-Flame">
<text>Daniel Kretschmer (born 19 September 1971), better known by his stage-name D-Flame, is a German hip hop and reggae musician. He was also previously part of the hip hop formation Asiatic Warriors.

